{"id":299485,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-中央巡视组接待六百余名在京访民（图）/","date":"2013-06-17T15:32:46Z","modified":"2013-06-17T15:32:46Z","title":"维权网 | 中央巡视组接待六百余名在京访民（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，中央巡视组在京接待了来自全国各地访民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span>多人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据北京暴力拆迁受害人葛志慧透露：今天有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span>多名访民云集“海淀区中关村友谊宾馆”的中央巡视组驻地。巡视组的官员们热情接待了来访群众，接收了他们递交的材料，承诺一定会转交中央。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午，葛志慧等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>名访民代表向中央巡视组递交了来自全国各地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多名访民签名，反映目前普遍存在的各级信访机构不按照《信访条例》的规定出具受理凭证等信访部门不作为，严重侵害信访人权利的现象；要求中央敦促查处信访部门的不法行为，维护党和政府的形象，维护老百姓的利益。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>巡视组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>名官员热情接待了葛志慧等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>名访民代表，了解了他们反映的问题，接收了他们递交的材料，承诺让他们放心，一定会把他们的材料和反映的问题上报中央。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，此次中央巡视组在京公开接待访民和接收访民递交的材料，时间截止至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，节假日不休息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中央巡视组在京接待访民的地址：海淀区中关村友谊宾馆侧门乡院律师楼（平房）。乘车路线：地铁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>号线地铁人大站</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span><span>出口</span><span></span><span>，也可乘坐公交</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>通信地址：北京市海淀区中关村南大街</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100086</span><span>信箱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 36</span><span>分箱（邮政编码</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100086</span><span>），中央第一巡视组收。专门值班电话：（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">010</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">68498365</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13241231270</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>葛志慧：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13261499836</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图：等待中央巡视组接待的部分访民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-w24rlNafOLg/Ub8kKG89vqI/AAAAAAAAjlw/LVhnGRraIQ0/s1600/tu+.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-w24rlNafOLg/Ub8kKG89vqI/AAAAAAAAjlw/LVhnGRraIQ0/s320/tu+.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}